  <!-- EN: Jade bamboo blade【Third-rate】 -->
  <RI_Weapon_JadeBambooBlade.label>苍血刀【三品】</RI_Weapon_JadeBambooBlade.label>
  <!-- EN: 【Third-rate】Range weapon\n\nGreen blood bamboo is a material that can carry spiritual energy very well. Weapons made of green blood bamboo and spiritual stone have limited damage in melee combat, but can trigger the energy blade to kill the enemy at long range.\n\nJade bamboo blade, can release a powerful long-distance energy cut, cut the enemy.\n\n<color=#FFFF00>【Special effects】Basic projectile armor penetration +25%.</color> -->
  <RI_Weapon_JadeBambooBlade.description>【三品】远程兵器\n\n苍血竹这种原料可以很好的承载灵气。用苍血竹和灵石打造的兵器，其近战杀伤力虽然有限，但可激发出兵刃之气，远程杀伤敌人。\n\n苍血刀，可释放出威力强大的刀气，斩击敌人。\n\n【特殊效果】发射物护甲穿透+25%。</RI_Weapon_JadeBambooBlade.description>
  <!-- EN: point -->
  <RI_Weapon_JadeBambooBlade.tools.point.label>刀尖</RI_Weapon_JadeBambooBlade.tools.point.label>
  <!-- EN: edge -->
  <RI_Weapon_JadeBambooBlade.tools.edge.label>刀刃</RI_Weapon_JadeBambooBlade.tools.edge.label>
  <!-- EN: Jade bamboo blade【Third-rate】 -->
